{"tid":2453453,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"鉅仔做Deal, 誠哥最終贏家; 大家可能睇漏依個位","createTime":"2021-03-19T12:45:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T10:18:33.000Z","uid":246729,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"6d2f9ab75ce37d4ed1029e2b8f767573cb66fadb","tid":2453453,"uid":246729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T12:45:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2910027/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2910027%2F&d=gmuJ%2FMz5RLkHlhSkJihz%2BbZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=73dd33a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2910027/</a><br />\n<em><blockquote>【長實│利好】李嘉誠李澤鉅新招增持長實 長實170億收購李嘉誠基金會資產、溢價近一成回購 承諾派息不減<br />\n李嘉誠、李澤鉅父子變相增持長實 （01113） ，長實公布，擬動用170億元現金從李嘉誠基金會收購4項基建資產，包括長實已經持有的公用公司Northumbrian Water、Wales &amp; West Utilities 及 Dutch Enviro Energy經濟權益。長實表示，建議收購符合公司既定企業策略，加強穩定收入來源，同時承諾交易作實後，今年股息不會較去年減少。<br />\n主席李澤鉅稱，完成交易可以令「股價靚仔啲」。據長實通告，完成交易後，李嘉誠、李澤鉅持股會由35.99%，增至45.02%。獨立股東會由64%減至54.97%。實際操作上，長實會以支付股份向李嘉誠基金會發行3.33億股份，每股作價51元。同一時間，長實會以每股51元的回購並註銷最多為股份數目上限的股份，即3.33億股股份。回購價格較連續10個交易日長實股價溢價1成，較今日收市價47.05元，就溢價8.4%。</blockquote></em><br />\n====================================================<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BUGTJMU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBUGTJMU.png&h=ab4e75ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n樓上facebook 千頌C 都講得七七八八<br />\n===================================================<br />\n但我有少少野補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有網友喺fb 留言: 「睇唔透。李嘉誠基金會點解會將啲好嘢賣比長實集團」<br />\n<br />\n睇嚟唔少人諗左一樣野<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.marketwatch.com/story/ofgem-proposes-cutting-returns-for-power-networks-2021-03-11\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.marketwatch.com%2Fstory%2Fofgem-proposes-cutting-returns-for-power-networks-2021-03-11&d=gmuJ%2FMz5RLkHlhSkJihz%2BbZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=ea2af95a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.marketwatch.com/story/ofgem-proposes-cutting-returns-for-power-networks-2021-03-11</a><br />\n<em><blockquote>Ofgem's working assumptions include setting the baseline return on equity at 4.4% CPIH, which is on average a third lower than under the current price control -- set at 7% if adjusted to a comparable basis.<br />\n</blockquote></em>"},{"pid":"eed650674dc0e9d451c2f73ca43eb1334cd3c519","tid":2453453,"uid":246729,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T12:46:17.000Z","msg":"三張CKI 長建嘅PPT 按次序分別係: 20190731 ; 20210317 ; 20200318<br />\n<br />\n第一張PPT<br />\n『Regulators  are  looking to  squeeze allowed cost of equity』<br />\n 『Need to balance affordability for customers, environmental concerns and incentives for investors to  continue investing into infrastructure』<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YXZ2B70.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYXZ2B70.png&h=016f054c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCost of equity 表面睇就係公司問股東拎資金嘅成本，但其實調轉諗，咪就係 return of equity (shareholder)<br />\n唔明？再解釋下： 公司發債，比債息，對公司嚟講就係 cost of debt； 對債劵持有人嚟講，就係return of bond investment<br />\n所以第一張圖講到明，監管當局要壓低股東回報<br />\n<br />\n第二張PPT<br />\n講到明嚟緊利潤管制(already started)<br />\n正正就係今次李嘉誠基會賣比1113嘅野<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zCk9g70.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzCk9g70.png&h=e67d748d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家自己睇圖, 今次1113 向 李嘉誠基金會買嘅係咩project?<br />\n幾時開始利潤管制? 仲係咪靚project? 未來業務仲有無前景?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AWGXq2v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAWGXq2v.png&h=75996793&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第三張PPT<br />\n監管當局：睇住你WACC 幾多去比你地賺幾多<br />\nCost of equity 下降，咪就係 return of shareholder下降<br />\n2005年 7.7% 到2020年3.1% 賣比大家(1113)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/26HSZmk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F26HSZmk.png&h=9cafb899&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同誠哥做 Counterparty，賺嘅向來只有得佢，The one &amp; only one <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5839fba5f23dc188abd9b9fc6b52bf89cd5c79e","tid":2453453,"uid":246729,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T12:46:47.000Z","msg":"唔記得有無喺公開場合講過, 其實1113 係嚴重under value<br />\nGreen King: 剛assets impairment, 但其實土地重建價值無寫落Book<br />\n1113 幾塊酒店地都入左紙/計劃緊/重建做住宅 &amp; 寫字樓 (天水圍=住宅 / 馬鞍山=住宅 / 紅磡=寫字樓)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n現時依一刻全部酒店地皮都係用 Historical Price 入帳, 第日重建完成, 價值體現<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2617844\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2617844&d=gmuJ%2FMz5RLkHlhSkJihz%2BbZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=e85f6b5e\" target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2617844</a><br />\n紅磡2酒店擬重建商廈 增218萬呎商業樓面<br />\n<a href=\"https://paper.hket.com/article/2826772/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpaper.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2826772%2F&d=gmuJ%2FMz5RLkHlhSkJihz%2BbZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=8f107663\" target=\"_blank\">https://paper.hket.com/article/2826772/</a><br />\n馬鞍山海澄軒獲批改劃純住宅 長實兩酒店成功改劃 共涉5758伙<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2831398\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2831398&d=gmuJ%2FMz5RLkHlhSkJihz%2BbZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=226959f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2831398</a><br />\n長實嘉湖海逸酒店改建5000伙住宅 規劃署不反對<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2350796\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2350796&d=gmuJ%2FMz5RLkHlhSkJihz%2BbZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=3308f46f\" target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2350796</a><br />\n長實鶴園街建商廈 周五城規會審議<br />\n<br />\n仲有好多野1113 係收埋左個價值, 好明顯 李澤鉅/誠哥 好清楚自己公司value 應該係幾多<br />\n<br />\n今次嘅交易<br />\n誠哥 本身持有緊36% undervalue 緊嘅1113<br />\n佢用四個無增長空間/甚至利潤會下跌嘅project, 去換多 8% undervalue 緊嘅1113 (完成後, 達45%)<br />\n而當中誠哥係自己唔洗出錢 <br />\n本身1113嘅股東，就係本身undervalue 嘅1113擁有權細左（樓上賺錢嘅酒店賣地）<br />\n而，多左四舊唔賺錢嘅project<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><ins><span class=\"x-large\">記住, 老闆思維, 易地而處,<br />\n企喺對方嘅角度諗下, 就會知到點解要咁做</span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「睇唔透。李嘉誠基金會點解會將啲好嘢賣比長實集團」<br />\n咁應該識答?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n-完-"},{"pid":"da59f21e56ff128d86bf0a2addf4404bfba24447","tid":2453453,"uid":246729,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T12:49:15.000Z","msg":"6號仔唔靠發電？ 唔洗交香港稅？(2019 04 07)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lookitsmathbook.blogspot.com/2019/04/6.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flookitsmathbook.blogspot.com%2F2019%2F04%2F6.html&d=gmuJ%2FMz5RLkHlhSkJihz%2BbZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=1e606aaf\" target=\"_blank\">https://lookitsmathbook.blogspot.com/2019/04/6.html</a><br />\n<br />\n睇李數簿...1038長江基建..鉅仔 (2019 04 26)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lookitsmathbook.blogspot.com/2019/04/1038.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flookitsmathbook.blogspot.com%2F2019%2F04%2F1038.html&d=gmuJ%2FMz5RLkHlhSkJihz%2BbZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=72d78fb8\" target=\"_blank\">https://lookitsmathbook.blogspot.com/2019/04/1038.html</a><br />\n<br />\n香港首隻物流房託上線啦: 順豐房託<br />\n<a href=\"https://lookitsmathbook.blogspot.com/2021/02/SFREIT.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flookitsmathbook.blogspot.com%2F2021%2F02%2FSFREIT.html&d=gmuJ%2FMz5RLkHlhSkJihz%2BbZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=1ce2cc9e\" target=\"_blank\">https://lookitsmathbook.blogspot.com/2021/02/SFREIT.html</a><br />\n<br />\nIB Max Draw Down-Excel Model 更新 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lookitsmathbook.blogspot.com/2020/12/max-draw-down-excel-model-2.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flookitsmathbook.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F12%2Fmax-draw-down-excel-model-2.html&d=gmuJ%2FMz5RLkHlhSkJihz%2BbZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8